      "start_time": 320786.0,
      "end_time": 323189.0,
      "text": "Because they paid to make your life easier."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 323222.0,
      "end_time": 324724.0,
      "text": "Like, if I was one of these kids,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 324757.0,
      "end_time": 326659.0,
      "text": "now I would be questioning everything good"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 326692.0,
      "end_time": 328594.0,
      "text": "that happens to me in life."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 328627.0,
      "end_time": 330996.0,
      "text": "Like, if one of my good-looking classmates hit on me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 331290.0,
      "end_time": 333399.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d be like, \"You don&#39;t really like me."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 333432.0,
      "end_time": 335368.0,
      "text": "\"You&#39;re just my dad in a wig."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 335401.0,
      "end_time": 337269.0,
      "text": "\"Give me that hair! Give me that hair!"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 337302.0,
      "end_time": 338704.0,
      "text": "\"Give me that...\" (imitates tearing sound)"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 338737.0,
      "end_time": 341400.0,
      "text": "\"Aah, aah, aah! Oh, wow. It was real."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 341730.0,
      "end_time": 342608.0,
      "text": "\"Uh, Dad, I did it again."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 342641.0,
